'''Uxbeg''' was a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] and rival to [[Lo Khan]]. Uxbeg was contracted to deliver a shipment of [[Spice/Legends|spice]] to [[Spadda]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]], but was kept busy while delivering a load of bulk [[yeast paste]] to [[Stars' End/Legends|Stars' End]] in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. Lo Khan arranged to intercept the spice shipment and deliver it himself.

